### BEGIN NOTMUCH-MUTT SETTINGS
    macro index <F8> \
        "<enter-command>unset wait_key<enter><shell-escape>~/.mutt/mutt-notmuch.pl --prompt search<enter><change-folder-readonly>~/.cache/mutt_results<enter>" \
